name: taobao.wlb.imports.order.get
description: 一般进口物流订单获取

requestParams.name: gmt_create_start
requestParams.description: 交易订单开始创建时间

requestParams.name: gmt_create_end
requestParams.description: 交易订单结束创建时间

requestParams.name: status_code
requestParams.description: 物流订单状态编码。以下依（物流订单状态编码，描述）的形式列举出来：(TIN_CONSING,发货中),(SENT_WAIT_COMPANY_MAKE_SURE,待仓库收货),(ORDER_CANCELED,订单关闭),(COMPANY_MAKE_SURE,海外仓已揽收),(REJECTED_RECEIVED_BY_COMPANY,海外仓拒收),(ORDER_REFUNDING,退货中),(ORDER_REFUND_BY_COMPANY,订单已退货),(EXCEPTION_IN_COMPANY,海外仓内异常),(FAILED_PAID_SHIPPING_FEE,支付失败),(PAID_SHIPPING_FEE,待仓库发货),(COMPANY_CONSIGN_CONFIRM,海外仓已发货),(WAIT_CUSTOMS_MAKE_SURE,清关已收货),(EXCEPTION_IN_CUSTOMS,清关异常),(CUSTOMSING,清关中),(COMPANY_DELIVERY,国内配送)。

requestParams.name: page_no
requestParams.description: 页码。取值范围:大于零的整数; 默认值:1

requestParams.name: page_size
requestParams.description: 每页条数。取值范围:大于0小于等于100的整数; 默认值:40; 最小值：1；最大值:20
